2006-03-02  Richard Sandiford  <richard@codesourcery.com>

	* elf32-i386.c (elf_i386_vxworks_link_output_symbol_hook): Delete.
	(elf_backend_link_output_symbol_hook): Use
	elf_vxworks_link_output_symbol_hook instead.
